{"word":"διαβαίνω","slug":"διαβαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διαβαίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διά\">διά</a>, βαίνω</el> ‘stride’, the basic idea of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διαβαίνω\">διαβαίνω</a></el> is legs separated in movement; the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> generally functions spatially ‘go through’] <b><i>cross over</i> <a href='B:490 16:26'>Lk 16:26</a>; <a href='B:650 11:29'>Hb 11:29</a>.—</b>διαβὰς <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a> <i>come over to</i> <b><a href='B:510 16:9'>Ac 16:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Δία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:διαβάλλω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}